## Frag grenade
EditTag objects\weapons\grenade\frag_grenade\frag_grenade.physics_model

SetField RigidBodies[0].ShapeType Pill

AddBlockElements Pills
SetField Pills[*].Name grenade_body
SetField Pills[*].RuntimeMaterialType 55
SetField Pills[*].RelativeMassScale 1
SetField Pills[*].Friction 0.85
SetField Pills[*].Restitution 0.3
SetField Pills[*].Volume 0.000192807
SetField Pills[*].Mass 0.382389
SetField Pills[*].PhantomIndex -1
SetField Pills[*].ProxyCollisionGroup -1
SetField Pills[*].ShapeBase.Count 128
SetField Pills[*].ShapeBase.ShapeType 3
SetField Pills[*].ShapeBase.Radius 0.0338
SetField Pills[*].Bottom 0 1.01E-10 -0.01441501
SetField Pills[*].BottomRadius 0.0338
SetField Pills[*].Top 0 1.01E-10 0.02230411
SetField Pills[*].TopRadius 0.0195

RemoveBlockElements Polyhedra 0 *
RemoveBlockElements PolyhedronFourVectors 0 *
RemoveBlockElements PolyhedronPlaneEquations 0 *
RemoveBlockElements Lists 0 *
RemoveBlockElements ListShapes 0 *

SaveTagChanges
Exit

