## Plasma grenade
EditTag objects\weapons\grenade\plasma_grenade\plasma_grenade.physics_model

SetField RigidBodies[0].ShapeType Sphere

AddBlockElements Spheres
SetField Spheres[*].Name grenade
SetField Spheres[*].RuntimeMaterialType 60
SetField Spheres[*].RelativeMassScale 1
SetField Spheres[*].Friction 0.85
SetField Spheres[*].Restitution 0.3
SetField Spheres[*].Volume 0.0001505325
SetField Spheres[*].Mass 0.2257988
SetField Spheres[*].PhantomIndex -1
SetField Spheres[*].ProxyCollisionGroup -1
SetField Spheres[*].ShapeBase.Count 128
SetField Spheres[*].ShapeBase.ShapeType 3
SetField Spheres[*].ShapeBase.Radius 0.033
SetField Spheres[*].ConvexBase.Count 128
SetField Spheres[*].ConvexBase.ShapeType 12
SetField Spheres[*].ConvexBase.Radius 0.033
SetField Spheres[*].ShapeReference.Shapetype Sphere

RemoveBlockElements Polyhedra 0 *
RemoveBlockElements PolyhedronFourVectors 0 *
RemoveBlockElements PolyhedronPlaneEquations 0 *

SaveTagChanges
Exit

## Firebomb grenade
